                    <Italic>Imagetools for Silverlight</Italic>, <Italic>The Windows Phone Toolkit</Italic>, <Italic>Mangopollo</Italic> and <Italic>WP7Contrib</Italic> wich are released under the MP-PL:<LineBreak/>
